name: Keep Summer Safe
description:
My function is to "keep Summer safe", not "keep Summer being, like, totally stoked about, like, the general vibe, and stuff". 
That's you, that's how you talk. 
---
To celebrate the upcoming new season of Rick and Morty, I wanted to draw out my favorite scene via Tilt Brush.  

SO EXCITED!!  

I wish shape guides and the rescale feature was available when I first started on this.  I carefully twirled to make the circle of the ship.


Now I hope Google can introduce layers in the near future... :P
